Anda bilang:
buatkan component untuk list pengalaman kerja saya
ChatGPT bilang:

Tentu! Saya bisa buatkan contoh React component untuk menampilkan list pengalaman kerja. Saya buat versi fleksibel yang bisa digunakan di proyek Next.js atau React biasa. Kita akan buat dengan props agar mudah diisi datanya.

Berikut contohnya:

tsx
"use client";

import React from "react";

type Experience = {
  company: string;
  position: string;
  startDate: string;
  endDate?: string; // bisa diisi undefined jika masih bekerja
  description?: string;
};

type ExperienceListProps = {
  experiences: Experience[];
};

const ExperienceList: React.FC<ExperienceListProps> = ({ experiences }) => {
  return (
    <section className="my-8">
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Pengalaman Kerja</h2>
      <ul className="space-y-6">
        {experiences.map((exp, idx) => (
          <li
            key={idx}
            className="p-4 border rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition"
          >
            <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 className="text-xl font-semibold">{exp.position}</h3>
              <span className="text-gray-500 text-sm">
                {exp.startDate} - {exp.endDate || "Sekarang"}
              </span>
            </div>
            <p className="text-gray-700 font-medium">{exp.company}</p>
            {exp.description && (
              <p className="text-gray-600 mt-2">{exp.description}</p>
            )}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </section>
  );
};

export default ExperienceList;

Penjelasan:

  • flex flex-col md:flex-row: stacked di mobile, sejajar di desktop.

  • space-y-6 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6: jarak vertikal di mobile, jarak horizontal di desktop.

  • flex-1: membuat kedua container sama lebar.

  • max-w-5xl mx-auto: membatasi lebar keseluruhan supaya tidak terlalu melebar di layar besar.

ChatGPT bilang:

Oke! Kita bisa samakan style Education seperti WorkExperience: card putih, shadow, responsive, logo di kiri (desktop) dan info di kanan, tinggi & lebar sama saat desktop. Saya buatkan versi baru Education component:

tsx
"use client";

import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from "react";

interface PendidikanItem {
  tahun: string;
  institusi: string;
  logo?: string;
  jurusan?: string;
  keterangan?: string;
}

interface PendidikanProps {
  data: PendidikanItem[];
}

export default function Education({ data }: PendidikanProps) {
  const containerRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);
  const [visible, setVisible] = useState(false);

  useEffect(() => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      ([entry]) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) setVisible(true);
      },
      { threshold: 0.3 }
    );
    if (containerRef.current) observer.observe(containerRef.current);
    return () => observer.disconnect();
  }, []);

  if (data.length === 0) return null;

  const item = data[0]; // hanya kuliah

  return (
    <div
      ref={containerRef}
      className={`w-full h-full p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-700 ease-out transform ${
        visible ? "opacity-100 translate-y-0" : "opacity-0 translate-y-10"
      }`}
    >
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center border-b border-gray-300 pb-2">
        Education
      </h2>

      <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center h-full">
        {/* Logo */}
        {item.logo && (
          <img
            src={item.logo}
            alt={item.institusi}
            className="w-16 h-16 object-contain mr-0 sm:mr-4 mb-2 sm:mb-0"
          />
        )}

        {/* Info */}
        <div className="flex-1">
          <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center">
            <h3 className="text-xl font-semibold">{item.institusi}</h3>
            <span className="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1 sm:mt-0">
              {item.tahun}
            </span>
          </div>
          {item.jurusan && (
            <p className="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">{item.jurusan}</p>
          )}
          {item.keterangan && (
            <p className="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">{item.keterangan}</p>
          )}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

Fitur baru:

  • Layout mirip WorkExperience: logo di kiri, info di kanan di desktop.

  • Responsive: stacked di mobile, sejajar di desktop.

  • Card background putih (bg-white) + shadow + padding.

  • Tinggi menyesuaikan parent, sehingga bisa sama tinggi saat di desktop berdampingan.

ChatGPT bilang:

Kalau logonya tidak muncul, biasanya ada beberapa penyebab yang sering kejadian di React + Next.js:

  1. Path/URL salah

    • Kalau logoUrl kamu pakai path lokal (misalnya "/public/logo.png"), di Next.js yang benar cukup "logo.png" atau "/logo.png". Semua file statis harus ada di folder public/.

    • Contoh: public/unindra.png → maka logoUrl="/unindra.png".

  2. Next.js pakai <Image />

    • Kalau kamu pakai next/image, harus impor dulu:

      tsx
      import Image from "next/image";

      lalu pakai:

      tsx
      <Image 
  src={edu.logoUrl} 
  alt={`${edu.institusi} logo`} 
  width={64} 
  height={64} 
  className="object-contain rounded-md"
/>

      Ini lebih aman daripada <img /> karena Next.js optimasi gambar.

  3. Kalau URL dari luar (misalnya logo LinkedIn)

    • Kamu harus tambahkan domain gambar di next.config.js bagian images.domains.

    • Contoh:

      js
      module.exports = {
  images: {
    domains: ["upload.wikimedia.org", "example.com"],
  },
};

✅ Jadi kalau logonya lokal dari folder public/, cukup pastikan kamu isi datanya gini:

    jurusan: "Teknik Informatika",
    tahun: "2020 - Sekarang",
    keterangan: "Semester 5"
  }
];

Kita bisa pakai flex + overflow-x-auto di desktop. Contoh perbaikannya:

tsx
"use client";

import React from "react";

type Experience = {
  company: string;
  logoUrl?: string;
  position: string;
  startDate: string;
  endDate?: string;
  description?: string;
};

type ExperienceListProps = {
  experiences: Experience[];
};

const ExperienceList: React.FC<ExperienceListProps> = ({ experiences }) => {
  return (
    <section
      className="
        my-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md
        w-[90%] sm:w-[85%] md:max-w-4xl
        mx-auto
      "
    >
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Work Experience</h2>

      {/* Mobile: list biasa, Desktop: scroll horizontal */}
      <ul
        className="
          space-y-6 md:space-y-0
          md:flex md:space-x-6
          md:overflow-x-auto
          md:scroll-snap-x md:snap-mandatory
        "
      >
        {experiences.map((exp, idx) => (
          <li
            key={idx}
            className="
              flex flex-col items-center text-center
              p-4 border rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition bg-white
              md:min-w-[300px] md:max-w-[300px] 
              md:snap-center
              flex-shrink-0
            "
          >
            {exp.logoUrl && (
              <img
                src={exp.logoUrl}
                alt={`${exp.company} logo`}
                className="w-16 h-16 object-contain mb-4 rounded-md"
              />
            )}
            <div className="flex-1">
              <h3 className="text-xl font-semibold">{exp.position}</h3>
              <span className="text-gray-500 text-sm">
                {exp.startDate} - {exp.endDate || "Sekarang"}
              </span>
              <p className="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">{exp.company}</p>
              {exp.description && (
                <p className="text-gray-600 mt-2">{exp.description}</p>
              )}
            </div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </section>
  );
};

export default ExperienceList;

✨ Penjelasan perubahan:

  • Mobile: tetap space-y-6 → list vertikal biasa.

  • Desktop (md ke atas):

    • flex overflow-x-auto → jadi scroll horizontal.

    • md:min-w-[300px] → tiap card punya lebar fix (hanya 1–2 card terlihat).

    • scroll-snap → biar pas di-scroll berhenti rapi di tiap card.

    • Default tampil index pertama, sisanya bisa di-scroll.

tsx
"use client";

import React from "react";

type EducationItem = {
  company: string;
  logoUrl?: string;
  jurusan?: string;
  date: string;
  description?: string;
};

type EducationListProps = {
  education: EducationItem[];
};

const EducationList: React.FC<EducationListProps> = ({ education }) => {
  return (
    <section
      className="
        my-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md
        w-[90%] sm:w-[85%] md:max-w-3xl
        mx-auto
      "
    >
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Education</h2>

      {/* Area scroll dengan border tipis */}
      <div
        className="
          border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4
          md:max-h-[400px] md:overflow-y-auto
        "
      >
        <ul className="space-y-6">
          {education.map((edu, idx) => (
            <li
              key={idx}
              className="
                flex flex-col items-center text-center
                p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition bg-white
              "
            >
              {edu.logoUrl && (
                <img
                  src={edu.logoUrl}
                  alt={`${edu.company} logo`}
                  className="w-16 h-16 object-contain mb-4 rounded-md"
                />
              )}
              <div className="flex-1">
                <h3 className="text-xl font-semibold">{edu.company}</h3>
                <span className="text-gray-500 text-sm">{edu.date}</span>
                {edu.jurusan && (
                  <p className="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">
                    {edu.jurusan}
                  </p>
                )}
                {edu.description && (
                  <p className="text-gray-600 mt-2">{edu.description}</p>
                )}
              </div>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  );
};

export default EducationList;
